'''Lisa''' is a surgical intern at Seattle Grace Hospital.

==History==
===Domino Kidney Transplant===
Lisa worked on the domino kidney transplant. She was one of the doctors who attended to [[Stan Mercer]] before his transplant. ''("[[There's No 'I' in Team]]")''

==Career==
She is a [[General Surgery|surgical]] [[Internship|intern]] at [[Seattle Grace Hospital]].
